	(10, 16, 1, 'Insulationg Glass Molecular Sieve', 'insulationg-glass-molecular-sieve', NULL, NULL, 'These sieves are used to absorb moisture and other trace gases, Moisture Absorption，Gas Purity Maintenance，Longevity', 'Insulationg Glass Molecular Sieve', 'these sieves are used to absorb moisture and other trace gases that could compromise the performance and longevity of the sealed air or gas-filled space between the panes.', 1, '/uploads/images/product/_1717137668_e3AvFDsCnQ.jpg', '/uploads/images/product/_1717395559_2uYbiJnDZR.jpg', '/uploads/images/product/_1717395559_SfuPmbfWKU.jpg', '/uploads/images/product/_1717395559_ZlMvlPoz8E.jpg', '/uploads/images/product/_1717395559_MOgxLiOHiV.jpg', '<h2 style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-block: 0.67em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The Role of Molecular Sieves in Insulating Glass</h2><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto hidden; text-wrap: wrap; margin-block-end: 1em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space-collapse: preserve !important; word-break: break-word !important;">Molecular sieves are porous materials with a controlled pore structure that selectively absorbs or adsorbs certain molecules. In the context of insulating glass, these sieves are used to absorb moisture and other trace gases that could compromise the performance and longevity of the sealed air or gas-filled space between the panes.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto hidden; text-wrap: wrap; margin-block-end: 1em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space-collapse: preserve !important; word-break: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/images/article/1_1717487156_VUfIj85XN7.jpg"/></p><h3 style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-block: 0.67em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Key Functions of Molecular Sieves in Insulating Glass</h3><ol style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-block-start: 1em; padding-inline-start: 2em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Moisture Absorption</span>: By adsorbing moisture, molecular sieves prevent the formation of condensation and fogging between the glass panes, which can degrade the insulating properties and clarity of the glass.</p></li></ol><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto hidden; text-wrap: wrap; margin-block-end: 1em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space-collapse: preserve !important; word-break: break-word !important;">2.<span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Gas Purity Maintenance</span>: They help maintain the purity of the gas (usually argon or krypton) used between the glass layers, which is critical for optimal thermal insulation.</p><ol style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-block-start: 1em; padding-inline-start: 2em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Longevity</span>: The use of molecular sieves extends the lifespan of insulating glass by preventing chemical reactions that can lead to the deterioration of the seal over time.</p></li></ol><h2 style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-block: 0.67em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Types of Molecular Sieves Used in Insulating Glass</h2><ol style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-block-start: 1em; padding-inline-start: 2em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: visible; white-space-collapse: preserve !important; word-break: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Type 3A</span>: Effective for the removal of water vapor, this type is commonly used in insulating glass units.</p></li><li><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: visible; white-space-collapse: preserve !important; word-break: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Type 4A</span>: Offers a higher capacity for water vapor adsorption compared to Type 3A and is used in environments with high humidity.</p></li><li><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: visible; white-space-collapse: preserve !important; word-break: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Type 5A</span>: With a larger pore size, this type is used for applications requiring the adsorption of larger molecules or where faster kinetics are needed.</p></li><li><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: visible; white-space-collapse: preserve !important; word-break: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">13X</span>: Known for its high selectivity and capacity for water vapor, it is used in specialized applications where extreme moisture control is necessary.</p></li></ol><h2 style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-block: 0.67em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Benefits of Using Molecular Sieves in Insulating Glass</h2><ol style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-block-start: 1em; padding-inline-start: 2em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: visible; white-space-collapse: preserve !important; word-break: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Enhanced Thermal Efficiency</span>: By keeping the gas space dry and free of impurities, molecular sieves help insulating glass maintain its thermal resistance.</p></li><li><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: visible; white-space-collapse: preserve !important; word-break: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Improved Acoustic Insulation</span>: The dry environment provided by molecular sieves contributes to better soundproofing properties.</p></li><li><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: visible; white-space-collapse: preserve !important; word-break: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Durability</span>: The inclusion of molecular sieves in insulating glass units results in a more durable product that requires less maintenance.</p></li><li><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: visible; white-space-collapse: preserve !important; word-break: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Environmental Benefits</span>: The use of molecular sieves in insulating glass contributes to energy savings and reduced environmental impact.</p></li></ol><p><br/></p>', '2024-05-31 06:34:44', '2024-06-04 08:25:22'),
	(11, 16, 1, 'Automobile Brake System Molecular Sieve', 'automobile-brake-system-molecular-sieve', NULL, NULL, 'Air Brake Molecular Sieve is used specially for air-actuated braking systems in cars, trucks, train and ship', 'Automobile Brake System Molecular Sieve', 'Air Brake Desiccant possess the high strength and H2O adsorption capacity, the low dust contamination and attrition resistance required withstanding high vibration.', 0, '/uploads/images/product/_1717398444_Md55jHQBXx.jpg', '/uploads/images/product/_1717396611_zwm63N2ry4.jpg', '/uploads/images/product/_1717398395_wFpN8o9W4b.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<p>Air Brake Molecular Sieve is used specially for of desiccation of air-actuated braking systems in cars, trucks, train and ship. Air Brake Desiccant possess the high strength and H2O adsorption capacity, the low dust contamination and attrition resistance required withstanding high vibration.</p><p><img src="/uploads/images/article/1_1717398376_PUQAvCiCsV.jpg" width="800" height="800" alt="" style="width: 800px; height: 800px;"/></p>', '2024-05-31 07:37:38', '2024-06-03 07:07:24'),
	(12, 16, 1, 'XH Molecular Sieve For Refrigeration', 'xh-molecular-sieve-for-refrigeration', NULL, NULL, 'The XH type molecular sieve plays a crucial role in refrigeration systems, with main applications including Desiccant,Purifying Agent,Catalyst Carrier...', 'XH Molecular Sieve For Refrigeration', 'The XH type molecular sieve is a synthetic zeolite material with a highly regular microporous structure.', 0, '/uploads/images/product/_1717141379_lLYFdtxit7.jpg', '/uploads/images/product/_1717396563_qx60mC4Wla.jpg', '/uploads/images/product/_1717396563_ezSZZlF8tk.jpg', '/uploads/images/product/_1717396563_dB4PW5Cnvs.jpg', '/uploads/images/product/_1717396563_BXwwnNkAQm.jpg', '<h2 style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-block: 0.67em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Composition and Characteristics of XH Type Molecular Sieve</h2><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto hidden; text-wrap: wrap; margin-block-end: 1em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space-collapse: preserve !important; word-break: break-word !important;">The XH type molecular sieve is a synthetic zeolite material with a highly regular microporous structure. This unique structure endows it with the following characteristics:</p><ol style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-block-start: 1em; padding-inline-start: 2em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">High Adsorption Capacity</span>: The XH type molecular sieve has a higher adsorption capacity than traditional molecular sieves, effectively adsorbing moisture and impurities in the refrigerant.</p></li><li><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Fast Adsorption Rate</span>: Its microporous structure is designed to optimize adsorption kinetics, making the adsorption process more rapid.</p></li><li><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Thermal Stability</span>: The XH type molecular sieve remains stable within the temperature range of the refrigeration system operation, not prone to decomposition or deactivation.</p></li><li><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Chemical Resistance</span>: It has good tolerance to refrigerants and common chemicals found in systems.</p></li></ol><h2 style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-block: 0.67em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Application of XH Type Molecular Sieve in Refrigeration Systems</h2><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto hidden; text-wrap: wrap; margin-block-end: 1em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space-collapse: preserve !important; word-break: break-word !important;">The XH type molecular sieve plays a crucial role in refrigeration systems, with main applications including:</p><ol style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-block-start: 1em; padding-inline-start: 2em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Desiccant</span>: Adsorbs moisture in the refrigerant to prevent system blockages and corrosion.</p></li><li><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Purifying Agent</span>: Removes acidic substances and other pollutants in the refrigerant, extending the life of the system.</p></li><li><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Catalyst Carrier</span>: In some refrigeration systems, molecular sieves can also serve as catalyst carriers, enhancing system efficiency.</p></li></ol><h2 style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-block: 0.67em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Advantages of XH Type Molecular Sieve</h2><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto hidden; text-wrap: wrap; margin-block-end: 1em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space-collapse: preserve !important; word-break: break-word !important;">Compared to traditional desiccants, the XH type molecular sieve has the following advantages:</p><ul style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-block-start: 1em; padding-inline-start: 2em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Longer Service Life</span>: Due to its high adsorption capacity and stability, the XH type molecular sieve has a longer service life.</p></li><li><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">Higher System Efficiency</span>: By effectively removing moisture and impurities, the XH type molecular sieve helps to improve the COP (Coefficient of Performance) of the refrigeration system.</p></li><li><p><span style="box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;">More Environmentally Friendly</span>: Compared to traditional desiccants, the XH type molecular sieve has a smaller environmental impact, meeting modern environmental requirements.</p></li></ul><h2 style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-block: 0.67em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Conclusion</h2><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto hidden; text-wrap: wrap; margin-block-end: 1em; color: rgb(6, 6, 7); font-family: -apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, helvetica, &quot;segoe ui&quot;, arial, roboto, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, miui, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); white-space-collapse: preserve !important; word-break: break-word !important;">As an advanced adsorbent material for refrigeration systems, the XH type molecular sieve offers new possibilities for the development of refrigeration technology with its efficient, stable, and environmentally friendly characteristics. With the growing demand for energy-efficient and environmentally friendly refrigeration systems, the application prospects for the XH type molecular sieve are broad.</p><p><br/></p>', '2024-05-31 07:42:59', '2024-06-03 07:21:28'),
	(13, 16, 1, 'Nitrogen Molecular Sieve', 'nitrogen-molecular-sieve', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Nitrogen Molecular Sieve', NULL, 0, '/uploads/images/product/_1717141456_ciC9Y926WA.jpg', '/uploads/images/product/_1717396458_b8t20OyKmZ.jpg', '/uploads/images/product/_1717396458_yCrCAyvCHJ.jpg', '/uploads/images/product/_1717396458_emzMD7qxPz.jpg', '/uploads/images/product/_1717396458_Hb2Oc9ZZJQ.jpg', '<p>Carbon molecular sieve is a new kind of adsorbent, which is an excellent non-polar carbon material. It is mainly composed of elemental carbon and appears as a black columnar solid. Carbon molecular sieve contains a large number of micropores, these micropores on the instantaneous affinity of oxygen molecules is strong, can be used to separate O2 and N2 in the air. In industry, pressure swing adsorption device (PSA) is used to make nitrogen. Carbon molecular sieve has the characteristics of strong nitrogen generating capacity, high nitrogen recovery rate and long service life. It’s suitable for various types of pressure swing adsorption nitrogen generator.s</p>', '2024-05-31 07:44:16', '2024-06-03 08:27:00'),
